caller_intent: The caller wants to cancel their car insurance policy because they moved to Arkansas and received a DMV notice that their license plates were canceled.
resolution_steps: Agent acknowledged the caller's request to cancel the policy due to relocation and license plate cancellation.
Agent offered to transfer the caller to a specialist who can assist with policy cancellation.
knowledge_required: Policy cancellation procedures for moving out of state
Handling license plate cancellation-related insurance adjustments
summary: A customer contacted Alliance Insurance to cancel their car insurance policy after moving to Arkansas and receiving a DMV notice about canceled license plates. The agent acknowledged the request and offered to transfer the caller to an agent who can process the cancellation.
